import React from "react";
import {
  Container,
  Form,
  FormGroup,
  Input,
  Label,
  Col,
  FormText,
  Button,
} from "reactstrap";
const SignUp = () => {
  return (
    <Container className="p-5">
      <Form>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Col lg={3}></Col>
          <Label for="name" sm={3} lg={1}>
            Name
          </Label>
          <Col sm={9} lg={5}>
            <Input
              id="name"
              name="name"
              placeholder="Enter your name"
              type="text"
            />
          </Col>
          <Col lg={3}></Col>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Col lg={3}></Col>
          <Label for="empid" sm={3} lg={1}>
            Employee Id
          </Label>
          <Col sm={9} lg={5}>
            <Input
              id="empid"
              name="empid"
              placeholder="Enter your Employee id"
              type="text"
            />
          </Col>
          <Col lg={3}></Col>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Col lg={3}></Col>
          <Label for="username" sm={3} lg={1}>
            Email Id
          </Label>
          <Col sm={9} lg={5}>
            <Input
              id="username"
              name="username"
              placeholder="Enter your Email id"
              type="text"
            />
          </Col>
          <Col lg={3}></Col>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Col lg={3}></Col>
          <Label for="phone" sm={3} lg={1}>
            Phone
          </Label>
          <Col sm={9} lg={5}>
            <Input
              id="phone"
              name="phone"
              placeholder="Enter your Contact number"
              type="text"
            />
          </Col>
          <Col lg={3}></Col>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Col lg={3}></Col>
          <Label for="password" sm={3} lg={1}>
            Email Id
          </Label>

          <Col sm={9} lg={5}>
            <Input
              id="password"
              name="password"
              placeholder="Enter Password"
              type="text"
            />
          </Col>
          <Col lg={3}></Col>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup check row className="justify-content-md-center">
          <Col
            sm={{
              offset: 2,
              size: 10,
            }}
            lg={{
              offset: 8,
              size: 4,
            }}
          >
            <Button>Submit</Button>
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
      </Form>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default SignUp;
